<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="blame-n">blame <strong><em>n</em></strong> ★</h1>
<p>英 /bleɪm/    美 /bleɪm/  </p>
<p>[U]</p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>( 对错误 / 坏事应负的) 责任； 责备</strong></h4>
<p>responsibility for a mistake or sth bad：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>take</strong> / <strong>bear the blame</strong> 
承担责任</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Where does the <strong>blame for</strong> our failure lie? 
我们失败的症结在哪里？</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Lots of people find it hard to get up in the morning, and <strong>put the blame on</strong> the alarm clock.
很多人发现早上起床很难，就把责任推到闹钟上。</p><footer>2017 全国</footer></div></div>